This used to fill the encountered UDFs when fillling comment subject and Body
The header is filled with the following format:
UDFName.UDFType. The UDF type can have one of the below values 1- Free_Text 2- ComboBox 3- CheckBox
Specify the value in the value field. In case the type is checkbox you can only use one of the below values: 1- Y 2- N
